H.4 verify (2026-05-14):

Scope: throughput — bump POLL_BATCH_SIZE default 50→100 + Lambda
       self-invocation chain. When a sweep drains a full batch
       (scanned === POLL_BATCH_SIZE), the kicker fires an async
       Lambda InvokeCommand against itself with chainDepth+1 so
       more due rows are processed without waiting for the next
       1-min EventBridge tick. Cap at POLL_MAX_CHAIN_DEPTH (5)
       hops per tick.

